{
  "stem": "26358.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Well, these Gestapos, when they come in, they like money.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And sometime you can buy yourself out with the money.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Not for long, but more you can longer be.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I think, thanks to that guy, my father accumulated money, sold lots of stuff.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And when they took me in concentration camp, I have enough money to pay-- as I-- we should come-- not him alone, like, but a dozen girls.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We paid what we can go home nights to sleep.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That be in the barracks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That was worth.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We used to go every morning-- 5, 6 o'clock go home, and 6-- and 5 o'clock go back.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "At 6 o'clock, we need to be in camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "First, we used to wash the clothes from the people what was working there in the concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was very bad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Where they made the camp was a monastery-- was preachers and nuns.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I don't know what happened to them that converts to a camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And there was kettles-- big kettle, where they cooked for the pigs, for something still-- with wood under an oven.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we used to take the shirts, put the hot-- put water-- go to the pump-- carry buckets of water, throw it in that kettle, and throw in the clothes, put hot-- and the lice should come down.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "With spoons, we used to take out the shirts-- pick up with spoons.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And after that, we washed it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Put with spoon.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And with a spoon, we used to take out the lice in from the kettle.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "That's how bad it was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We used to work like that for six months, I think.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, [INAUDIBLE], we was--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, first we changed with the-- it was the police-- was Ukrainian police first that made it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We have a station.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
